<plot>LIEBERMANS IN THE SKY is an offbeat comedic journey through fatherhood, water beds and Cabalistic folklore. It is the story of Alan Lieberman, a beleaguered water bed salesman, on the worst day of his life. It is a story about failure and one man's journey towards realizing that, like levitation, there are some things in life we cannot achieve. Sometimes falling is just the way of the world.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?335165</url></doc>
